Day 74: Jenkins Database Backup Job

Date: November 15, 2025
Overview
Created automated database backup pipeline.
Key Concepts Learned

Backup automation
Artifact archiving
Post-build actions
Email notifications

Build Steps
bash#!/bin/bash
TIMESTAMP=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)
mysqldump -u root -p$DB_PASSWORD mydb > backup_$TIMESTAMP.sql
gzip backup_$TIMESTAMP.sql

Challenges Faced
Secure credential management for database passwords. Learned to use Jenkins Credentials plugin!
